'''Rosette Chantal Rugamba''' ni  umucuruzikazi washoye mu bukerarugendo, washinze kandi Umuyobozi wa Songa Africa, sosiyete ikora ibijyanye n'ubukerarugendo muri  Afurika y'Iburasirazuba akaba na  nyiri Amakoro Songa Kinigi Lodge ikorera  mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref>https://www.global-ambassadors.org/people/rosette-chantal-rugamba/</ref> <ref>https://www.cnbcafrica.com/2019/songa-africas-chantal-rugamba-on-the-rise-of-high-end-tourism-in-rwanda/</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Rosette afite impamyabumenyi ya politiki ( siyanse mbonezamubano) ya siyanse na sociologiya yakuye muri kaminuza ya Makerere, yize ibijyanye no kwamamaza mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] kandi ni umuyobozi wa Aspen's global leadership -Ali East Africa of 2010. <ref>https://eturbonews.com/56736/rosette-rugamba-graduates-aspen-s-global-leadership-course/</ref> Niwe mwanditsi w’isoko rusange ry’iburasirazuba n’Amajyepfo (COMESA) m'Ubukerarugendo burambye  - ishingiro ryo gushyiraho ingamba n’ubukerarugendo mu karere. <ref>https://equitygroupfoundation.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Equity-Bank-Annual-Report-2015-1.pdf</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Rosette Chantal Rugamba ashishikajwe cyane n'ubukerarugendo kandi afite ubutunzi bwinshi bw'ubushishozi n'inzego za leta mu gukangurira ubufatanye bwa Leta n'abikorera guteza imbere ubukerarugendo neza . Rosette yagize uruhare runini mu nganda n’ubukerarugendo mu myaka 24 ishize atangirana na EuroStar mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]], hanyuma aba umuyobozi ushinzwe kugurisha no kwamamaza muri British Airways muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]] no muri central Afurika . <ref>https://www.africanparks.org/about-us/our-people/rosette-chantal-rugamba</ref> , yagiye akora nk'Umuyobozi mu Nama Nyafurika yikorabuhanga- [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] . <ref>https://www.gianmarcomaraviglia.com/rwanda-women</ref> Ni perezida w’Urugereko rw’Ubukerarugendo, akaba n'umwe mu bagize inama y’Urugereko rw’Abagore mu Ishyirahamwe ry’abikorera. <ref>https://www.essence.com/lifestyle/travel/black-travel-guide/visiting-africa-community-led-tourism-airbnb-travel-summit/</ref> Kuva mu 2003, Rosette yagizwe umuyobozi mukuru w’ibiro by’ubukerarugendo na parike y’u [[Rwanda]] (ORTPN), <ref>https://womenforenvironment.org/we_are/rosette-chantal-rugamba/</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/4089</ref> aho yateje imbere ububyutse n’iterambere ry’ubukerarugendo mu nyuma makimbirane  y’u Rwanda no kubungabunga parike eshatu z’igihugu mu [[Rwanda]] . <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/46460</ref> <ref>http://expressnews.rw/rosette-rugamba-gets-appointed-to-unwtos-tourism-ethics-committee/</ref> Kuva mu 2003 kugeza 2010, ubwo yari umuyobozi ushinzwe ubukerarugendo no kubungabunga ibidukikije mu [[Rwanda]], umubare w’abakerarugendo wiyongereye uva ku 13.000 ugera kuri 790.000 ndetse anaba uwa mbere mu kwinjiza amadovize. <ref>https://www.tourismleadershipforum.africa/2018-speakers-details/</ref> [[Rwanda|U Rwanda]] rwatoranijwe kuba intangarugero mu gukora ubukerarugendo bwa  [[Afurika]] kandi rutsindira imurikagurisha ryiza rya [[Afurika]] mu imurikagurisha ry’ubucuruzi rya ITB-tourism mu myaka 4 ikurikiranye. <ref>https://www.balancingact-africa.com/news/telecoms-en/5467/rwanda-is-selected-as-model-for-e-tourism</ref> Rosette yamenyekanye [[Umuryango w’Ibihugu by’Iburasirazuba bw’Afurika|nk'Ubunyamabanga bw'Afurika y'Iburasirazuba]] nk'umwe mu bashinzwe ubukerarugendo no kubungabunga ibidukikije mu karere. Yabaye umuyobozi mukuru wungirije ushinzwe ubukerarugendo no kubungabunga [[Ikigo gishinzwe iterambere mu Rwanda|Ikigo cy’iterambere ry’u Rwanda]] (RDB). <ref>https://eturbonews.com/29395/deputy-ceo-rwanda-development-board-tourism-moves/</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/88607</ref> Rosette Rugamba ashyirwa muri komite ishinzwe imyitwarire y’ubukerarugendo bwa UNTWO-Global manda  y’imyaka ine yatangiye ku ya 17 Nzeri 2017 kandi akora nk'umujyanama wihariye w’umunyamabanga mukuru w’umuryango w’abibumbye ushinzwe ubukerarugendo ku isi (UNWTO). <ref>https://www.unwto.org/members-2017-2021</ref> <ref>https://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4084807.html</ref> Mu zindi nshingano za Rosette harimo gukorera mu Nama y'Ubucuruzi Mark East Africa (TMEA) na Sonarwa-Insurance Company. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/192042</ref>

